title: Except where the same are prescribed in Mumbai Municipal Corporation Act, 1888, or Maharashtra Regional and Town Planning Act, 1966 or the rules or bye-laws framed there under, the Commissioner may, from time to time, add to, alter or amend Appendices and Annexures appended to these Regulations
